<strong>Information on Government Officials</strong>
<p>Find out who your representatives are and how to contact them – everyone from your U.S. Senator to your state's governor and your representatives in the state legislature.</p>

<strong>YLI's Guide to Writing to an Elected Official</strong>
<p>Want to make sure politicians know what you think about the issues?  Use our guide to help write a letter to you elected official.</p>

<strong><a href="http://www.politicalmoneyline.com/" target="_blank">Search Campaign Finance Information</a></strong>
<p>Interested in finding out how candidates raise money to run for office?  Find information on the donations to candidates from individuals, corporations, and political action committees (PACs).</p>		</div>
