			<h2 style="text-align: center;">As high school students graduate and move on to college and the workforce they will need to keep themselves up to date on current events, this however is not always easy. Below we have given you all the tools high school graduates need to obtain the most up to date, non-biased, and accurate news possible.<a href="http://208.81.226.245/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/News-Handout.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-2375" src="http://208.81.226.245/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/News-Handout.png" alt="News Handout" width="975" height="1262" /></a></h2>
