                    				2. A vehicle with at least 50 miles per gallon will receive the same as above except the credit is increased to 20 percent.  <br><br />
                    				3. A vehicle with at least 60 miles per gallon will receive the same as the above except the credit is increased to 25 percent.  <br><br />
                    				4. No credit shall exceed $3,000</p>
